‼️Maternity leave announcement:‼️
I will be out of office from May 8th-mid July. 
This year i will not be putting out any mother’s day baked goods in preparation for baby Penelope. 

Thank you so much to all of my friends, family and followers for your support, consideration and patience during this special time. I look forward to connecting with y’all when I return. 🤰🏻👋🏼

I will remain active till then, to fulfill orders and share content 🎂

***BIRTHDAY 🧁🍰GIVEAWAY*** (CLOSED)

In honor of my upcoming birthday September 1st, I am giving away one dozen cupcakes or a 6” vintage style cake. 

All you need to do is;
1.) Like this photo, be following me (@danmaries.creations) 

2.) Add a comment below with your favorite cake flavor and tag a friend. Each tag in a separate comment is an additional entry~ 

3.) For 5 extra entries share this to your story ✨
*if you have a private account, please take a screenshot of your story* 

4.) I will choose two winners from a random name generator~ The winners can choose either a dozen cupcakes or a 6” vintage cake. 

***Giveaway Only open to Houston/surrounding area residents!!

The giveaway will end at 11:59pm Friday, September 1st and the winners will be picked the next day. Feel free to share this post with anyone who likes sweets~ Good luck!! :)
